<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>404 – Point Not Found</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      background: #fdfaf6;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      color: #444;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 50px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 60px;
      color: #b22222;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 20px;
    }
    .needle {
      margin: 30px auto;
      width: 120px;
      height: 120px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 6px dashed #b22222;
      position: relative;
      animation: pulse 1.5s infinite;
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.6; }
      50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 1; }
      100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.6; }
    }
    .home-button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      font-size: 18px;
      background-color: #b22222;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .home-button:hover {
      background-color: #8b1a1a;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="needle"></div>
  <h1>404 – Point Not Found</h1>
  <p>Like a misplaced meridian, this page doesn’t seem to exist.</p>
  <p>Return to balance and <a href="/" class="home-button">go home</a>.</p>
</body>
</html>